/* ==UserStyle==
@name           darkstar
@namespace      github.com/openstyles/stylus
@version        1.0.0
@description    A new userstyle
@author         Me
==/UserStyle== */

@-moz-document domain("") {
    /* Insert code here... */
}
:root {
	--bg-color: #292d3e !important;
	--bg-alt-color: #434758 !important;
	--fg-color: #bbc5ff !important;
	--link-color: #82aaff !important;
	--link-hover-cover: #c792ea !important;
	--border-color: #c792ea !important;
	--font: Mononoki !important;
}

/* width */
::-webkit-scrollbar {
	color: #292d3e !important;
}

* {
  	color: #bbc5ff !important;
 	background-color: transparent !important;
  	border-color: transparent !important;
  	font-family: Mononoki !important;
}

a,
a:visited,
span a,
.d-flex a,
clipboard-copy,
.btn,
.btn i {
	color: #82aaff !important;
}

a:hover,
.d-flex a:hover {
	color: #c792ea !important;
	text-decoration: none !important;
}

html,
body,
div,
div.commit-branches *,
div.commit.full-commit p.commit-title *,
qul.branches-list *,
.d-flex,
header,
#header,
footer,
#footer,
button,
a.button,
a.submit,
a.BigButton,
a.TabLink,
.install[onclick],
a[href="javascript:;"],
a[class*="button"]:not(:empty),
a[id*="button"]:not(:empty),
a[id*="Button"]:not(:empty),
div[class*="button"][onclick],
.fbNubFlyoutBodyContent,
[type|="submit"] {
	background-color: #292d3e !important;
  	color: #bbc5ff !important;
}

iframe,
embed,
header,
nav,
footer,
label [onclick],
nav ul,
div[style*="position:"][style*="left:"][style*="visible"],
div[style*="z-index:"][style*="left:"][style*="visible"],
div[style*="-moz-user-select"],
div[role="menu"],
div[role="dialog"],
div[id="task details"],
span[class*="script"] div,
[id*="menu"],
[class*="dropdown"],
[class*="popup"],
[class="title"],
[class="search__autocomplete"],
[class="top-matter"],
ul[style*="display:"],
ul[style*="visibility:"] ul,
[id*="nav"] ul,
[class*="nav"] ul,
ul[class*="menu"],
a[onclick][style*="display"],
a[id*="ghosteryfirefox"],
#ghostery-purple-bubble,
#translator-popup,
.menu,
.tooltip,
.hovercard,
.vbmenu_popup,
* .navigation,
* .navigation a,
menu,
dir,
.openData .odGradient,
.stable-head td div,
.rplm-alert .content-wrap,
#navbar *,
#sondage,
div.dlg-window,
.modal-container .modal-content .modal-box .once-modal,
.tabs_main ul li a,
.tabs_main ul li span,
.module-actionbar .module-actionbar-action,
.bg_01,
.bg-default,
.box-highlight,
.bg-brighter,
.mvxl,
#downloads,
.questions-ovl,
.ovl-frame,
.messenger__contacts .scroll,
.messenger__contacts .scroll_,
.messenger__content .scroll,
.messenger__content .scroll_,
.st_error .messenger__content-inner .scroll__,
a.info:hover span,
a.info:focus span,
#system,
#product,
.clicked,
.notClicked,
.notClicked:hover,
#ident_div_ident,
.idAbonne,
#pageFacture .tab-content,
span.conteneurTips,
.ligneOption,
.ligneMevo td,
[id*="footer"],
.modal-dialog,
.cadre-contenu,
#cart_summary,
#loyalty-target,
#cont-subnav,
.wrapper,
.filtre-thematiques-selected,
.filtre-thematiques,
ul.thematiques,
li.thematique.sans-chaines,
a.voir-thematique,
[class*="progTrigger"],
#connexion,
.sub-menu .sub-nav-article-wrapper,
#navMain ul li,
.SMainRack,
.STopRack,
.STopFirst,
.SBotRack {
  background: #292d3e !important;
  border-top-color: #c792ea !important;
}

.pagination .disable:hover,
.pagination a,
.markdown-body code,
.markdown-body table * code,
.markdown-body pre,
.markdown-body table * pre,
.subnav-links a:hover,
.user-profile-sticky-bar:after,
tr.Even,
div.thumbinner,
table.wikitable > * > tr > th,
.post h2,
.post div.entry blockquote,
.post div.entry kbd,
tr:hover,
blockquote,
pre,
.bottom-notice,
.question-status,
pre code,
.topbar-dialog .header,
.new-post-activity,
#sidebar .module.community-bulletin,
.newuser,
#ad502-room,
.post-signature,
.vote {
	background-color: #434758 !important;
}

input,
text-area,
input *,
select *,
::-webkit-input-placeholder {
	background-color: #434758 !important;
  	padding: 2px !important;
  	color: #bbc5ff !important;
  	text-align: center;
  	border-bottom-color: #c792ea !important;
  	border-radius: 25px !important;
}

img,
video {
	background-color:  transparent !important;
	border-radius: 10px !important;
}

.HeartAnimation,
.search-icon,
.css-truncate-target {
  background-color: transparent !important;
  color: #82aaff !important;
}

.stream-item {
  padding: 5px 10px 5px 10px !important;
  border-radius: 0px !important;
}

table,
h1,
h2,
h3,
h4,
h5,
h6 {
  	border-color: #c792ea !important;
  	padding: 10px !important;
	border-radius: 10px !important;
}

.file-wrap,
.pl-mi1,
.pl-md,
.commit-desc pre,
.commit-meta.commit-author-section,
.table-list-cell .commit-title,
a.tabnav-tab,
.tabnav-tab,
input#lst-ib,
#sb_ifc0.sbib_b,
#gs_taif0,
div.vectorTabs li.selected,
div.vectorTabs li.selected span,
.bg-black-050,
.val-info,
#tabs a {
	background-color: transparent !important;
}
